BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Panic Disorder) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 700.0 Td (Recurrent unexpected panic attacks followed by persistent worry about having more attacks.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 686.0 Td (Panic attacks involve sudden surges of intense fear with physical symptoms like chest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 672.0 Td (pain, shortness of breath, and feeling like you are dying.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 644.2 Td (Specific Phobias) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (Intense, irrational fear of specific objects or situations such as heights, flying,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (animals, blood, or enclosed spaces. The fear is out of proportion to the actual danger) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.2 Td (posed.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 572.4 Td (Health Anxiety) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (Preoccupation with having or developing a serious illness. Involves frequent body) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (checking, excessive research about symptoms, repeated doctor visits, or avoidance of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.4 Td (health-related information.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 498.6 Td (Physical Symptoms of Anxiety) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.8 Td (Anxiety is not just in your head. It produces real, measurable physical changes throughout) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.8 Td (your body. These symptoms occur because your sympathetic nervous system activates the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.8 Td (fight-or-flight response:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 419.0 Td (- Rapid heartbeat or heart palpitations) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 405.0 Td (- Shortness of breath or feeling like you cannot get enough air) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 391.0 Td (- Chest tightness or chest pain) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 377.0 Td (- Muscle tension, especially in neck, shoulders, and jaw) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 363.0 Td (- Stomach problems: nausea, butterflies, IBS symptoms) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 349.0 Td (- Sweating, especially palms, underarms, and forehead) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 335.0 Td (- Trembling or shaking) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 321.0 Td (- Dizziness or lightheadedness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 307.0 Td (- Tingling or numbness in hands and feet) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 293.0 Td (- Dry mouth and difficulty swallowing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 279.0 Td (- Headaches and migraines) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 265.0 Td (- Fatigue and exhaustion despite adequate sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 251.0 Td (- Insomnia or restless sleep) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 237.0 Td (- Frequent urination) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 223.0 Td (- Hot flashes or chills) Tj ET
