stream
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 720.0 Td (Believing something is true because you feel it strongly. Example: I feel like a failure,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 706.0 Td (so I must be one.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 678.2 Td (6. Should Statements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Rigid rules about how you, others, or the world should be. Example: I should never make) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (mistakes. People should always be on time.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 620.4 Td (7. Overgeneralization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Taking one negative event and applying it to all situations. Example: One bad date means) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (you will never find love.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 562.6 Td (8. Magnification and Minimization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.6 Td (Blowing negative things out of proportion while shrinking positives. Example: Focusing on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.6 Td (one piece of critical feedback while ignoring ten compliments.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 504.8 Td (9. Personalization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 488.8 Td (Taking responsibility for things that are not your fault. Example: My friend canceled) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 474.8 Td (plans, so it must be because of something I did wrong.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 447.0 Td (10. Filtering) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 431.0 Td (Focusing exclusively on negative details while filtering out all positive aspects of a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 417.0 Td (situation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 387.2 Td (How to Complete a Thought Record) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 359.4 Td (Follow these steps each time you notice anxiety rising:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 335.6 Td (- Step 1: Identify the SITUATION - What happened? Where were you? Who was there?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 321.6 Td (- Step 2: Record your EMOTIONS - What did you feel? Rate intensity 0-100%) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 307.6 Td (- Step 3: Capture AUTOMATIC THOUGHTS - What went through your mind?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 293.6 Td (- Step 4: Find the COGNITIVE DISTORTION - Which thinking error applies?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 279.6 Td (- Step 5: Challenge the thought with EVIDENCE FOR and AGAINST) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 265.6 Td (- Step 6: Create a BALANCED THOUGHT - A more realistic alternative) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 251.6 Td (- Step 7: RE-RATE your emotions - How do you feel now? 0-100%) Tj ET
endstream
