BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (Tracking your anxiety daily serves multiple important purposes. It helps you identify) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (patterns in when and why your anxiety increases or decreases. It shows you the connection) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (between your habits and your anxiety levels. And it provides concrete evidence of your) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (progress over time.) Tj ET
